{"tid":2006461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日咁重要一定要叫多啲人出去","createTime":"2020-05-07T19:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T02:12:02.000Z","uid":162268,"like":38,"dislike":206,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c87013ef5c067fde59973e49599adb1e4fbc7bab","tid":2006461,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/On5cnsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOn5cnsu.jpg&h=118ac43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實我哋唔需要出去<br />\n交俾我哋最信任嘅議員<br />\n同偉大嘅美國出手就得<br />\n<br />\n利申：真黃和理非，聽日要返工，兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命（外判）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9e458fed00ab60d5edf49737d19bdd66e6b54147","tid":2006461,"uid":162268,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:17:46.000Z","msg":"推，要多啲人手呀（人哋隻手）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7eb4351f619f5ac77ff4fa52119106a438bd17","tid":2006461,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:18:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2946a3ab07fcf4f01f85cd6c9fb406fb899a587","tid":2006461,"uid":74058,"like":26,"dislike":5,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:18:34.000Z","msg":"帶文具出街正傻仔"},{"pid":"da021b650997211ff5a32d997ecbc30c27eefb9d","tid":2006461,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:18:36.000Z","msg":"見到post嘅 唔該幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bde1e2c20a7448fc09951040eb6adb0e69e1d55","tid":2006461,"uid":162268,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"e2946a3ab07fcf4f01f85cd6c9fb406fb899a587","tid":2006461,"uid":74058,"like":26,"dislike":5,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:18:34.000Z","msg":"帶文具出